data.description: Welcome to your dream home at 13506 United Ln in the prestigious Stewarts Landing subdivision of Bowie. This stunning property boasts a perfect blend of elegance, functionality, and charm. With 4 spacious bedrooms and 3.5 bathrooms, this three-story gem offers ample space for your growing family. Step inside and be greeted by the warm and inviting atmosphere that permeates every corner of this home. The kitchen is a chef's delight, featuring top-of-the-line appliances, granite countertops, and an abundance of storage space.  Retreat to the luxurious primary suite, complete with a spa-like ensuite bathroom and a walk-in closet. Outside, the expansive .23-acre lot provides endless possibilities for outdoor activities and relaxation. The attached 2-car garage ensures convenience and security for your vehicles. With a prime location, open space and recreation behind the home, and easy access to shopping, dining, and entertainment, this property is the perfect home for you and your family. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this house your forever home. Schedule your private tour today!
